                style="
                  color: #000;
                  margin: 4px 0;
                  line-height: 1.5;
                  font-size: 14px;
                "
              >
                Start a Scorecard: Jump right into a decision you’re facing
                today and see how Decidifi’s structure helps simplify the
                process.
              </li>
              <li
                style="
                  color: #000;
                  margin: 4px 0;
                  line-height: 1.5;
                  font-size: 14px;
                "
              >
                Save and Revisit: Use your account to save progress and revisit
                scorecards as your decisions evolve.
              </li>
