                style="
                  color: #000;
                  margin: 4px 0;
                  line-height: 1.5;
                  font-size: 14px;
                "
              >
                Learn the Basics: If you have questions about how Decidifi works
                or want to explore its functionality, visit the How Decidifi
                Works tab—it’s a great place to start.
              </li>
