                  color: #000;
                  margin: 4px 0;
                  line-height: 1.5;
                  font-size: 14px;
                "
              >
                Refine and Revisit: Once saved, you can revisit your scorecard
                anytime to refine your decision as circumstances evolve.
              </li>
