              style="
                color: #000;
                margin: 15px 0;
                line-height: 1.5;
                font-size: 14px;
                           padding:0px 20px; "
            >
              While your access is limited to this scorecard, we occasionally
              create new scorecards for topics with broad appeal to our
              community. If there’s something specific you’re looking for, feel
              free to reach out—we’d love to hear from you.
